code: import axios from'axios';const url='http://localhost:8000/rol/api/v1/rol/';export const obtenerRoles=async()=>{const response=await axios.get(url);return response.data;};export const crearRoles=async rol=>{const response=await axios.post(url,rol);return response.data;};export const eliminarRoles=async id=>{const response=await axios.delete("http://localhost:8000/rol/api/v1/rol/".concat(id,"/"));return response.data;};export const actualizarRoles=async(id,rol)=>{const response=await axios.put("http://localhost:8000/rol/api/v1/rol/".concat(id,"/"),rol);return response.data;};
